203707196.Title: Samsung 30 in. W 21.8 cu. ft. French Door Refrigerator in Stainless Steel, Silver
203707196.Description: This beautifully compact stainless steel French door refrigerator offers a robust 22 cubic feet of interior space and at 33 inches wide. Bright LED lighting makes the fridge easy to view and organize and a wide-open pantry allows room for oversized food items that often don't fit elsewhere. It may be smaller in size, but this compact refrigerator doesn't compromise on style, space or performance.
